"```sql\nSELECT COUNT(*)\nFROM loan\nJOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id\nWHERE loan.duration = 24\n  AND account.frequency = 'POPLATEK TYDNE';\n```\n\nThis SQL query counts the number of loan accounts that have a loan duration of 24 months and a weekly issuance of statements, as indicated by the frequency value 'POPLATEK TYDNE'. The query joins the `loan` and `account` tables using the `account_id` foreign key relationship."